	•	Reads tracked fields from a JSON in blob.
	•	Compares incoming document (from change feed) against latest.
	•	Uses ETag for concurrency safety.
	•	Stores versioned blobs when a tracked field changes.
	•	Maintains a latest.json per document using index tags.

